  <p class="text-block justified">
    <b>About Project:</b> The goal of this project was to scrape the
    OSU MBB Roster page found
    <a href="https://ohiostatebuckeyes.com/sports/m-baskbl/roster/">
      here</a>. Some players' personal pages contain a "STATS"
    tab with their personal statistics. This project scrapes
    the main roster page, checks which players have a "STATS"
    tab on their personal page, and scrapes the statistics
    for each game played.
    <br/><br/>
    Data is then compiled into various graphs showing different
    aggregated statistics. For details on some of the calculations
    used, please see the About Game Scores section.
  </p>
